WEBVTT

00:00:00.039 --> 00:00:25.719
Subtitle Provide by dramacool.asia Translator [Admin.@YNG]

00:01:06.439 --> 00:01:08.719
Welcome to the Night King City auction.

00:01:09.239 --> 00:01:10.920
We hope everyone bids enthusiastically.

00:01:10.920 --> 00:01:11.760
Thank you for your support.

00:01:12.200 --> 00:01:13.879
The auction officially begins now.

00:01:14.920 --> 00:01:16.040
The first item up for auction

00:01:16.439 --> 00:01:17.719
is this piece of Glow Pearl Stone.

00:01:17.879 --> 00:01:19.879
Starting bid is 100,000 Glow Pearls.

00:01:20.680 --> 00:01:21.280
500,000.

00:01:21.640 --> 00:01:23.120
I'll bid to support Xiao Yue.

00:01:24.840 --> 00:01:25.159
Raise the bid.

00:01:26.599 --> 00:01:27.480
1,500,000.

00:01:29.560 --> 00:01:30.239
2,000,000.

00:01:31.760 --> 00:01:32.560
5,000,000.

00:01:35.519 --> 00:01:36.120
Lin Yue.

00:01:36.359 --> 00:01:37.359
Are you out of your mind?

00:01:37.640 --> 00:01:38.480
5,000,000, going once.

00:01:38.640 --> 00:01:39.519
5,000,000, going twice.

00:01:40.480 --> 00:01:41.480
5,000,000, going three times.

00:01:41.920 --> 00:01:42.359
Sold!

00:01:55.560 --> 00:01:57.400
Five million for a useless rock?

00:01:57.799 --> 00:01:59.680
Let's see how you explain this to the Sect.

00:02:01.760 --> 00:02:04.480
Let me show you something impressive.

00:02:06.359 --> 00:02:08.719
This stone is made of Mystic Silver.

00:02:09.039 --> 00:02:10.439
It's worth five million on its own.

00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:11.879
Not to mention,

00:02:16.919 --> 00:02:17.520
Look closely!

00:02:19.039 --> 00:02:19.800
A talisman!

00:02:19.879 --> 00:02:20.639
Besides,

00:02:21.639 --> 00:02:23.000
Inside this Mystic Silver,

00:02:23.400 --> 00:02:24.960
there's a top-tier talisman.

00:02:25.599 --> 00:02:28.400
It's one of a kind in the entire Hongmeng Continent.

00:02:30.560 --> 00:02:31.319
This talisman

00:02:31.479 --> 00:02:33.360
can be used for the Instant Universe Array.

00:02:33.879 --> 00:02:36.919
It allows instant teleportation anywhere.

00:02:37.759 --> 00:02:40.719
Looks like Brother Lin is determined to get this talisman.

00:02:43.000 --> 00:02:45.400
It's good to have it for emergencies.

00:02:47.280 --> 00:02:48.360
The second auction item

00:02:48.919 --> 00:02:50.080
is an Ancient Divine Sword.

00:02:50.240 --> 00:02:52.520
A master craftsman spent thirty years

00:02:52.680 --> 00:02:54.120
forging it from Starmetal.

00:02:54.479 --> 00:02:55.520
Its power is incredible.

00:02:56.000 --> 00:02:58.319
Starting bid is one million Glow Pearls.

00:02:58.680 --> 00:02:59.360
Six million.

00:02:59.520 --> 00:03:00.120
Seven million.

00:03:00.400 --> 00:03:01.280
Eight million.

00:03:01.520 --> 00:03:02.479
Ten million.

00:03:03.479 --> 00:03:04.599
You again?

00:03:06.080 --> 00:03:06.879
Twenty million.

00:03:07.039 --> 00:03:08.479
Young Master, calm down.

00:03:08.759 --> 00:03:09.199
Fine.

00:03:09.439 --> 00:03:11.159
We'll buy this sword another time.

00:03:13.000 --> 00:03:13.879
With your skills,

00:03:14.080 --> 00:03:15.639
stop pretending to be rich.

00:03:16.439 --> 00:03:16.960
Wait.

00:03:18.479 --> 00:03:19.039
Brother Lin,

00:03:19.520 --> 00:03:20.680
just keep bidding.

00:03:21.080 --> 00:03:21.639
I'll cover the money.

00:03:23.039 --> 00:03:23.879
I'll pay for it.

00:03:26.479 --> 00:03:28.199
I appreciate your kindness, Brother Qin.

00:03:28.919 --> 00:03:29.520
But

00:03:30.080 --> 00:03:31.000
there's no need

00:03:31.000 --> 00:03:32.479
to argue with that idiot.

00:03:32.680 --> 00:03:33.800
The auction has just started.

00:03:33.960 --> 00:03:34.960
We should save our strength.

00:03:35.479 --> 00:03:36.319
You're the idiot.

00:03:38.599 --> 00:03:39.520
Twenty million, going once.

00:03:40.680 --> 00:03:41.479
Twenty million, going twice.

00:03:42.919 --> 00:03:43.919
Twenty million, going three times.

00:03:45.000 --> 00:03:45.560
Sold!

00:03:45.719 --> 00:03:46.439
Alright, alright!

00:03:46.560 --> 00:03:47.879
Young Master Lei is so cool!

00:03:50.759 --> 00:03:51.240
Xiao Yue,

00:03:51.680 --> 00:03:52.960
do you see my strength now?

00:03:58.520 --> 00:03:59.759
This Fairy Sword requires weapon bonding.

00:04:00.120 --> 00:04:01.120
Someone like you

00:04:01.400 --> 00:04:02.680
probably can't even draw it.

00:04:05.080 --> 00:04:05.919
Fairy Sword.

00:04:06.960 --> 00:04:08.439
Young Master Lei, you don't know?

00:04:08.719 --> 00:04:09.719
I bought this sword

00:04:10.039 --> 00:04:12.159
to give to our Sect Leader Qin Ji.

00:04:12.159 --> 00:04:13.159
It's a gift.

00:04:13.439 --> 00:04:14.960
Why did you buy this sword?

00:04:16.040 --> 00:04:17.040
I'm so handsome,

00:04:21.040 --> 00:04:22.199
how dare you mess with me!

00:04:22.600 --> 00:04:24.000
You were the one who bid.

00:04:24.240 --> 00:04:25.560
How can you blame Young Master Lin?

00:04:25.839 --> 00:04:26.439
Young Master,

00:04:26.560 --> 00:04:27.439
let him go.

00:04:28.720 --> 00:04:30.079
You can't beat him anyway.

00:04:31.319 --> 00:04:32.000
Let go of me!

00:04:39.040 --> 00:04:40.160
The third auction item

00:04:40.319 --> 00:04:42.439
is the treasured artifact of Night King City.

00:04:42.639 --> 00:04:43.839
The Ancient Secret Key.

00:04:45.040 --> 00:04:45.879
That's it.

00:04:46.360 --> 00:04:48.759
Starting bid: twenty million Glow Pearls.

00:04:49.279 --> 00:04:51.360
This is Night King City's heirloom.

00:04:51.920 --> 00:04:53.920
There's a way to keep it from leaving the family.

00:04:53.920 --> 00:04:55.879
Whoever wins the treasure

00:04:56.199 --> 00:04:58.120
will marry Ye Mingyue.

00:04:58.480 --> 00:05:00.639
If the treasure goes to the son-in-law,

00:05:00.879 --> 00:05:02.319
it's not considered passing it to outsiders.

00:05:02.959 --> 00:05:03.519
Brother Lin,

00:05:04.199 --> 00:05:05.839
do you know the origin of this key?

00:05:06.160 --> 00:05:07.040
Of course I do.

00:05:07.600 --> 00:05:08.160
And

00:05:08.720 --> 00:05:10.000
I also know how to use it.

00:05:10.720 --> 00:05:11.360
Luo Yixue,

00:05:12.079 --> 00:05:12.759
place a bid.

00:05:13.560 --> 00:05:14.439
How much?

00:05:14.839 --> 00:05:16.040
Twenty-five million.

00:05:16.879 --> 00:05:18.399
We don't have that much money, do we?

00:05:19.000 --> 00:05:20.079
Just bid as I say.

00:05:24.439 --> 00:05:25.560
Twenty-five million.

00:05:28.959 --> 00:05:30.480
I may not know how to use it,

00:05:30.920 --> 00:05:32.079
but Night King City's treasure

00:05:32.079 --> 00:05:34.639
can't end up in the hands of a country bumpkin.

00:05:34.839 --> 00:05:35.839
Thirty million.

00:05:39.120 --> 00:05:40.079
Forty million.

00:05:40.480 --> 00:05:41.399
Fifty million.

00:05:41.639 --> 00:05:42.319
Sixty million.

00:05:42.639 --> 00:05:43.079
Sevâ€”

00:05:44.480 --> 00:05:45.240
Sixty-one million.

00:05:46.839 --> 00:05:47.800
Eighty million.

00:05:48.720 --> 00:05:50.079
Show us your eighty million first.

00:05:50.600 --> 00:05:51.639
If you can't,

00:05:51.959 --> 00:05:53.240
that's fraud.

00:05:54.079 --> 00:05:55.240
I'll pay for him.

00:05:58.759 --> 00:06:00.000
Sect Leader.

00:06:02.800 --> 00:06:03.639
So,

00:06:04.160 --> 00:06:06.480
you really know how to use this key, huh?

00:06:07.240 --> 00:06:08.160
Thank you, Sect Leader.

00:06:08.560 --> 00:06:09.480
Of course I do.

00:06:11.560 --> 00:06:13.680
There are too many people and eyes here.

00:06:13.920 --> 00:06:14.680
How about

00:06:14.920 --> 00:06:17.399
we find a quiet place to talk?

00:06:17.600 --> 00:06:18.519
I'll follow your arrangements.

00:06:20.560 --> 00:06:21.839
Discussing such an important secret,

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:23.720
how could you leave out the Young Sect Leader?

00:06:25.639 --> 00:06:26.079
Let's go.

00:06:26.600 --> 00:06:27.160
Lin Yue,

00:06:29.560 --> 00:06:31.360
you stole my woman and cheated me out of money.

00:06:31.600 --> 00:06:32.720
Now you're stealing my spotlight.

00:06:33.759 --> 00:06:34.879
I'm settling all scores with you.

00:06:35.360 --> 00:06:35.879
Lei Zong,

00:06:36.600 --> 00:06:37.639
don't be so arrogant.

00:06:38.279 --> 00:06:40.160
Your sect's swapping of the Saintess

00:06:40.639 --> 00:06:41.759
can't be hidden from me.

00:06:42.160 --> 00:06:42.800
Jun Wushang,

00:06:43.399 --> 00:06:45.279
you sold the city's treasure to an outsider.

00:06:45.279 --> 00:06:46.480
What right do you have to lecture me?

00:06:46.680 --> 00:06:48.399
Today, I insist on killing him.

00:06:56.240 --> 00:06:56.800
Young Sect Leader!

00:07:00.639 --> 00:07:01.160
Young Sect Leader!

00:07:01.600 --> 00:07:03.759
The Sect Leader of Lei Yun Sect is as strong as Jun Wushang.

00:07:04.079 --> 00:07:05.000
If his son is killed,

00:07:05.240 --> 00:07:07.040
this kid won't live much longer.

00:07:07.040 --> 00:07:09.000
He's gotten himself into big trouble.

00:07:09.199 --> 00:07:10.959
Father, you saw it all.

00:07:11.160 --> 00:07:12.600
Young Master Lin was forced to fight back.

00:07:12.839 --> 00:07:13.800
I saw everything.

00:07:14.720 --> 00:07:15.399
But

00:07:15.959 --> 00:07:18.040
Sect Leader Lei definitely won't let this go.

00:07:18.879 --> 00:07:20.000
Even without this incident,

00:07:20.439 --> 00:07:21.759
Lei Yun Sect Leader Lei Long

00:07:22.079 --> 00:07:23.279
would come for us anyway.

00:07:23.879 --> 00:07:25.120
Young Master Lin,

00:07:25.680 --> 00:07:27.759
you should leave Night King City quickly.

00:07:27.959 --> 00:07:29.959
You've already got what you wanted.

00:07:30.199 --> 00:07:30.839
No rush.

00:07:31.319 --> 00:07:32.720
There's something I truly want

00:07:33.000 --> 00:07:33.839
still to come.

00:07:36.279 --> 00:07:38.040
You're pretty calm, aren't you?

00:07:39.160 --> 00:07:41.639
Aren't you afraid Lei Long will come for you?

00:07:42.759 --> 00:07:44.360
I'm not someone who fears trouble.

00:07:44.600 --> 00:07:46.639
You really don't know your limits.

00:07:47.279 --> 00:07:49.600
Do you know Lei Yun Sect Leader Lei Long's level?

00:07:49.759 --> 00:07:50.800
Ninth Rotation Realm.

00:07:51.600 --> 00:07:53.000
And you're only at the Salvation Realm.

00:07:53.439 --> 00:07:55.319
He could kill you easily.

00:07:56.560 --> 00:07:57.839
I'm no match for him.

00:07:58.160 --> 00:07:58.759
But

00:07:59.079 --> 00:08:00.000
I have help.

00:08:00.920 --> 00:08:01.680
What help?

00:08:02.600 --> 00:08:03.759
Heaven's secrets must not be revealed.

00:08:04.720 --> 00:08:05.319
Sect Leader Ye,

00:08:05.959 --> 00:08:06.879
you came

00:08:07.040 --> 00:08:08.560
for the Annihilation Cosmic Staff, right?

00:08:16.439 --> 00:08:17.439
Except for this kid,

00:08:18.279 --> 00:08:19.319
everyone else, step back.

00:08:20.040 --> 00:08:20.519
Step back.

00:08:20.519 --> 00:08:21.079
Yes.

00:08:27.560 --> 00:08:29.120
You're still so young,

00:08:29.800 --> 00:08:31.600
how do you know about the Annihilation Cosmic Staff?

00:08:33.440 --> 00:08:34.440
The Annihilation Cosmic Staff

00:08:34.679 --> 00:08:36.080
was left by one of the Three Emperors of the Upper Realm,

00:08:36.080 --> 00:08:37.399
Qi Tian Emperor.

00:08:37.559 --> 00:08:39.039
It has the power to sweep through armies.

00:08:39.399 --> 00:08:40.240
Rumor has it

00:08:41.159 --> 00:08:43.720
the Annihilation Cosmic Staff is hidden somewhere in Night King City,

00:08:44.639 --> 00:08:46.399
protected by a mysterious magic array.

00:08:47.240 --> 00:08:48.200
And your family

00:08:48.399 --> 00:08:50.360
has held the key to the array for generations.

00:08:51.440 --> 00:08:53.240
But even you

00:08:53.440 --> 00:08:55.200
don't know the exact location of the array.

00:08:55.360 --> 00:08:57.320
So you used the auction

00:08:58.120 --> 00:08:59.600
to lure those in the know.

00:09:09.200 --> 00:09:11.600
My daughter was right about you.

00:09:13.399 --> 00:09:15.600
Son-in-law, let's head to the array now.

00:09:15.600 --> 00:09:16.159
Alright.

00:09:16.600 --> 00:09:17.200
But

00:09:17.720 --> 00:09:19.279
I hope City Lord Ye will agree to one thing.

00:09:20.279 --> 00:09:21.000
What is it?

00:09:21.440 --> 00:09:23.080
After we get the Annihilation Cosmic Staff,

00:09:23.360 --> 00:09:24.639
I want to borrow it for a while.

00:09:25.200 --> 00:09:26.320
To accomplish something important.

00:09:26.679 --> 00:09:27.559
Once it's done,

00:09:27.759 --> 00:09:28.600
I will definitely return it.

00:09:40.639 --> 00:09:42.080
Who did this

00:09:44.240 --> 00:09:46.480
with such cruelty?

00:09:46.720 --> 00:09:47.480
It was Lin Yue.

00:09:50.679 --> 00:09:52.639
If I don't avenge this grudge,

00:09:54.679 --> 00:09:56.679
I swear I won't rest until I get revenge.